Here is a simple example that will insert the remote-address(!) via the `OnRecordBeforeCreateRequest` app hook (for more details how to extend PocketBase you can check the "Use as framework" guide):
```
// GO - https://pocketbase.io/docs/go-event-hooks/#onrecordbeforecreaterequest
app.OnRecordBeforeCreateRequest("yourCollection").Add(func(e *core.RecordCreateEvent) error {
// this is the only address you can trust out of the box
